---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hello World | Vipul Zope" description="My first blog post on my new personal website.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <a href="/blog" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline text-sm mb-6 inline-block">&larr; Back to Blog</a>

    <header class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Hello World</h1>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
        <time>June 29, 2026</time>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded text-xs">intro</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded text-xs">web</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>Welcome to my blog! This is my first post on <strong>vipulzope.in</strong> — a site I built to have my own little corner of the internet.</p>

      <h2>Why I Built This</h2>
      <p>I've always wanted a personal website, but kept putting it off. Today I finally sat down and made it happen. I used:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Astro</strong> — fast, modern, outputs static HTML</li>
        <li><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> — for styling without writing tons of custom CSS</li>
        <li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong> — free hosting, easy deployment</li>
        <li><strong>Formspree</strong> — for the contact form (no backend needed)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What's Coming</h2>
      <p>I plan to write about:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Things I'm building</li>
        <li>Tech I'm learning</li>
        <li>Problems I've solved</li>
        <li>Random thoughts on code and life</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>A Code Block for Good Measure</h2>
      <pre><code>const greeting = "Hello, World!";{'\n'}console.log(greeting);</code></pre>

      <p>Stay tuned for more posts. Thanks for reading!</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose :global(h2) { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .prose :global(p) { margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .prose :global(strong) { color: var(--color-text); }
  .prose :global(ul) { list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .prose :global(ol) { list-style: decimal; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .prose :global(li) { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .prose :global(pre) { background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1rem; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .prose :global(code) { background: var(--color-bg-card); padding: 0.2em 0.4em; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.875em; }
</style>
